      "raw_text": "Laborlng men!\n\n\nGo to Elks' Hall tonight\n\n\nHear the truth about Acutf, the corporation slave\ndriver\n\n\nListen to your brother union men-your\nneighbors-tell what they know about Acuff, the\nenemy of organized abor-the advocate of the\n\"open shop\"\n\n\nDo not fail to attend the labor rally tonight Be\nto go and learn why you asked to vote for\nDaggett, Eggleston and Farley.\n\n\nLearn to what you must do to defeat the Spokes-\nman Review S stool pigeon candidateH. H. Lilien-\nthai."
